{"about_the_game":"From the creators of DefleMask and Minimic , introducing Polybeep, a magnificent polyrhythmic sound machine designed to unlock your creativity.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189830/extras/1.png?t=1729276933\" /><br><br>With aesthetically pleasing colors and design alongside unmatched visual feedback, you can really feel the beeping beeps and the poly rhythms. Yes, you can set up polyrhythms as easy as 3-4-5.<br>When ready, you can save your songs and export them to wav files. We\u2019d love to hear the songs that you come up with! We even prepared a built-in tutorial to get you started.<br>Mobile version is also available! Polybeep has been designed with a touch screen in mind from day one.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189830/extras/2.png?t=1729276933\" /><br><br>You can record sounds directly from your microphone or load sample files. There\u2019s some magic to make them sound great. Arrange the sounds into up to 6 looping shapes that can be configured as polygons of 3~16 vertices, then tweak their effects (delay, reverb, EQ, panning, chorus, and more), make a sequence of many melodies, and you\u2019ll have a song in no time! You can even tap to change the tempo based on a rhythmic pulse.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189830/extras/3.png?t=1729276933\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3189830?t=1729276933","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3189830?t=1729276933","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189830/1dda3298de1074e7baad903f5a640bc2fee65e1e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729276933","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189830/1dda3298de1074e7baad903f5a640bc2fee65e1e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729276933","content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"From the creators of DefleMask and Minimic , introducing Polybeep, a magnificent polyrhythmic sound machine designed to unlock your creativity.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189830/extras/1.png?t=1729276933\" /><br><br>With aesthetically pleasing colors and design alongside unmatched visual feedback, you can really feel the beeping beeps and the poly rhythms. Yes, you can set up polyrhythms as easy as 3-4-5.<br>When ready, you can save your songs and export them to wav files. We\u2019d love to hear the songs that you come up with! We even prepared a built-in tutorial to get you started.<br>Mobile version is also available! Polybeep has been designed with a touch screen in mind from day one.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189830/extras/2.png?t=1729276933\" /><br><br>You can record sounds directly from your microphone or load sample files. There\u2019s some magic to make them sound great. Arrange the sounds into up to 6 looping shapes that can be configured as polygons of 3~16 vertices, then tweak their effects (delay, reverb, EQ, panning, chorus, and more), make a sequence of many melodies, and you\u2019ll have a song in no time! You can even tap to change the tempo based on a rhythmic pulse.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189830/extras/3.png?t=1729276933\" />","developers":["Pareidolabs"],"genres":[{"description":"Audio Production","id":"52"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189830/header.jpg?t=1729276933","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_